Installing
==========

1. `cd ~`
2. `git clone git://github.com/augustl/.emacs.d.git`
3. Optional machine-specific settings:
   - `cp ~/.emacs.d/local.example.el ~/.emacs.d/local.el`
   - Edit `local.el` (for example `augustl-font-height`) as needed.

Notes
=====

- `custom.el` and `local.el` are gitignored.
- `init.el` is checked in.
- No git submodules are required.
